{
  "texts": [
    " Evolutionary computation: It is not solely concerned with optimization problems; it relies upon the use of heuristics and representational paradigms.",
    "It allows machines to interpret and understand visual information from the world, such as images and videos.",
    " Natural Language Processing (NLP): NLP focuses on enabling machines to understand and interact with human language.",
    "It is used in chatbots, language translation, and voice recognition systems.",
    " Reinforcement Learning AI: This application of AI learns through trial and error, receiving feedback and rewards for its actions."
  ]
}